oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Man pictured with four largemouth bass taken from Harpeth River, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of W. Rye and four nice largemouth bass taken from the Harpeth River. Rye is sitting against a vehicle with fishing basket and the fish tied to the door handle. He is wearing a hat, shirt, pants and boots.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
